casebody.data:
Tony Orlando PINNIX
v.
STATE of North Carolina. No. 576P04. Supreme Court of North Carolina. December 2, 2004. Tony Orlando Pinnix, Pro Se. William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, Robert F. Johnson, District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Plaintiff on the 9th day of November 2004 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the North Carolina Court of Appeals, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 2nd day of December 2004."
